node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: You are literally doing your best... be proud of yourself for that. You’ve got this. ♥️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on July 22, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Take a deep breath and remember who the fuck you are.'.

node.text:
Lately I’ve been feeling like I’m suffocated by anxiety. So reading this made me stop to take a deep breath (may sound silly to some, but it’s actually helped me!). ♥️ 

@mentalhealthsquares

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on July 18, 2021 tagging @mentalhealthsquares. May be an image of text.
Photo by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on July 15, 2021.

node.text: Just a little reminder to be kind. Even when you’re hurting. Even when you don’t feel like it. Treat people in the way you need to be treated. It will always come back to you. You’ve got this. We need more kindness in this world full of hatred. ♥️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on July 12, 2021 tagging @theopeninvite. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'ከንE People don't realize how much strength it takes to pull your own self out of a dark place mentally. So, that if you've done today or any day, i'm proud of you. theopeninvite'.

node.text:
I’m proud of you. But you should be proud of yourself too. 

🎨 - @theopeninvite

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on July 08, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Feel the pain and let it go 🙌🏼♥️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on July 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '"But it made you stronger". was a child. I didn't need to be stronger. needed to be safe.'.

node.text:
If your childhood was full of fear and learning how to be strong, or you had to “grow up” too quick... I’m sorry. You deserved better. You deserved much, much better. 

Credit: unknown (please tag if you know who this belongs to).

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on July 04, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Tom Hulme @MindfulTom The lack of mental health education in school is shocking. It seems young people only learn about mental health after suffering from it themselves.'.

node.text:
There needs to be more mental health awareness in schools/college etc. Leave a “♥️” if you agree ♥️ 

📸 - @mindful_tom

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on July 04, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'NEVER STOP BEING A GOOD PERSON BECAUSE OF BAD PEOPLE'.
Photo by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on June 28, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: Be gentle with the person you are becoming ♥️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Self Love | Mental Health ♥ on June 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'hey when i come over to ur house can we just cry for like an hour Yeah obviously Read 11:54 PM'.

node.text: Okay, who else needs this right now? 🤔
